Sentencas: A-site deficient (La0.6Sr1.4)(0.95)Mn1-xBxO4 (x = 0, 0.1, B = Co, Ni, Cu) (LSMBO4) Ruddlesden-Popper oxides were demonstrated as promising symmetrical electrodes for Sc2O3 stabilized ZrO2 (SSZ) electrolyte supported solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Nanoscale architecture of (La0.6Sr1.4)0.95Mn0.9B0.1O4 (B=Co, Ni, Cu) Ruddlesden-Popper oxides as efficient and durable catalysts for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The formation of oxygen vacancies is facilitated with the B-site transition metal doping.
Titulo: Nanoscale architecture of (La0.6Sr1.4)0.95Mn0.9B0.1O4 (B=Co, Ni, Cu) Ruddlesden-Popper oxides as efficient and durable catalysts for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A-site defect promotes the exsolution of catalytic Co, Ni or Cu nanoparticles on the surface of materials in reducing atmosphere.
Titulo: Nanoscale architecture of (La0.6Sr1.4)0.95Mn0.9B0.1O4 (B=Co, Ni, Cu) Ruddlesden-Popper oxides as efficient and durable catalysts for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrochemical performances in air and reducing atmosphere are significantly optimized via the substitution of Mn by Co, Ni or Cu and exsolved metallic nanoparticle catalysts.
Titulo: Nanoscale architecture of (La0.6Sr1.4)0.95Mn0.9B0.1O4 (B=Co, Ni, Cu) Ruddlesden-Popper oxides as efficient and durable catalysts for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Especially, the materials doped by B-site with Cu shows the highest electrical conductivity of 37.54 S cm(-1) and 6.82 S cm(-1) and lowest polarization resistance of 0.12 Omega cm(2) and 0.32 Omega cm(2) at 750 degrees C in air and 5% H-2/N-2, respectively.
Titulo: Nanoscale architecture of (La0.6Sr1.4)0.95Mn0.9B0.1O4 (B=Co, Ni, Cu) Ruddlesden-Popper oxides as efficient and durable catalysts for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum power density of 623.1 mW cm(-2) at 750 degrees C is achieved for an electrolyte-supported symmetrical single cell with the LSMBO4-SSZ composite electrode operating with pure H-2.
Titulo: Nanoscale architecture of (La0.6Sr1.4)0.95Mn0.9B0.1O4 (B=Co, Ni, Cu) Ruddlesden-Popper oxides as efficient and durable catalysts for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: All these results indicate that LSMBO4 can be promising candidates for symmetric electrodes of SOFCs.
Titulo: Nanoscale architecture of (La0.6Sr1.4)0.95Mn0.9B0.1O4 (B=Co, Ni, Cu) Ruddlesden-Popper oxides as efficient and durable catalysts for symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells
